3. cs.CY (Computers and Society) - The paper may also be relevant to the societal implications of grid computing and the need for secure authentication mechanisms. 
4. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses the efficiency of certificate-less authenticated key agreement protocols, which may involve information theory concepts.
